node.text: In this episode of the Mac’s Minute, Colin shows the proper way to use the Mac’s threaded stud.

node.text:
A familiar voice on the latest episode of the @truckshowpodcast. Colin called in to the tow-isode to talk about common tie-down mistakes and choosing the proper equipment to correctly and safely protect your passion. #MacsTieDowns #TrustMacs 

Tap the link in our bio to listen.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mac's Tie Downs on July 23, 2021. May be an image of car and outdoors.

node.text: Low-lying vehicles make it difficult to access the front or rear axle. The Mac's Tire Block Strap Pack removes the need to get under the vehicle. The blocks and webbing only come in contact with the tire. #MacsTieDowns #TrustMacs

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mac's Tie Downs on July 22, 2021.

node.text: "I'd rather be driving it but when something is on the trailer I trust my Mac's Tie Downs to keep thing secure." - @mor_speed_shop  #MacsTieDowns #TrustMacs

node.text: #ICYMI, the @fna405 #Farmboat was spotted on the water. They're always thinking outside the box. But one thing remains constant: their trust in Mac's products to keep whatever they're building/hauling secure. #MacsTieDowns #TrustMacs

node.text: Like our automotive tie-down straps, Mac's 1" utility tie downs are completely customizable. And if you still can't find what you need, give us a call at 800-666-1586. No project is too big or too small. #MacsTieDowns #TrustMacs

node.text: Mac's is back on the road! If you're attending the @iolacarshow, be sure to stop by our display on the main drag, west of the tower. There's plenty of product on display and available for purchase. Trent and John can also help answer all your tie-down questions. #MacsTieDowns #TrustMacs #iolacarshow #iola21
